&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Full time &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Registered Dental Nurse to join our friendly team within our well established Oral Maxillo-Facial Surgery outpatient departments across our three hospital sites in Worcestershire. The successful applicant will be motivated and dynamic, with a willingness to learn new skills and keep up to date, whilst maintaining the highest clinical standards in their care. Experience in Orthodontics and working within a multi-disciplinary Oral Maxillo-Facial team are desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For any further information please do not hesitate to contact Sister Justine South on 01905 763333 ext: 30923 or via email justine.south@nhs.net or Matron Rachel Harris on 01905 763333 bleep 352 or email rachel.harris27@nhs.net.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interview date: Thursday 10th December&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
